To display the feasibility metrics separately in the GUI, we need to update the HTML to include placeholders for each feasibility metric and update the JavaScript to handle the array of feasibility values.

### Step 1: Update [`VeRyPy-GUI/verypy/gui/index.html`](VeRyPy-GUI/verypy/gui/index.html)

Add placeholders for the three feasibility metrics.

```html
<!-- filepath: /c:/Users/kskog/OneDrive/Tiedostot/.verypy-gui-dippa/VeRyPy-GUI/verypy/gui/index.html -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VeRyPy VRP Solver</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>VeRyPy VRP Solver</h1>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>Problem Input</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="vrp-file">Upload .vrp file</label>
                        <input type="file" id="vrp-file" accept=".vrp">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="coordinates">Coordinates</label>
                        <textarea id="coordinates" rows="5" placeholder="Enter coordinates (one per line, format: index x y)"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="customer-demands">Customer Demands</label>
                        <textarea id="customer-demands" rows="5" placeholder="Enter customer demands (one per line, format: index demand)"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="capacity">Vehicle Capacity (C)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="capacity" placeholder="Enter vehicle capacity constraint (optional)">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="L">Maximum route length/duration/cost (L)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="L" placeholder="Enter route length/duration/cost constraint (optional)">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                        <label for="single" style="margin-bottom: 0;">Single Iteration</label>
                        <input type="checkbox" id="single" checked>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                        <label for="minimize_K" style="margin-bottom: 0;">Minimize Number of Routes (K)</label>
                        <input type="checkbox" id="minimize_K">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="algorithm">Select Algorithm</label>
                        <select id="algorithm">
                            <option value="">Choose an algorithm</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <button id="solve">Solve VRP</button>
                    <button id="reset">Reset</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="column">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2>Solution Metrics</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <div class="statistics-grid">
                            <div>
                                <h3>Total Distance</h3>
                                <p id="total-distance">N/A</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3>Number of Routes</h3>
                                <p id="num-routes">N/A</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3>Computation Time</h3>
                                <p id="computation-time">N/A</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3>Covering Feasibility</h3>
                                <p id="covering-feasibility">N/A</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3>Capacity Feasibility</h3>
                                <p id="capacity-feasibility">N/A</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3>Route Cost Feasibility</h3>
                                <p id="route-cost-feasibility">N/A</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```

