2. **Set Up the Canvas**: Add a `<canvas>` element to the HTML and set up the canvas context in JavaScript.
3. **Draw the Points**: Draw the depot and customer points on the canvas.
4. **Draw the Routes**: Draw lines connecting the points in each route.

This approach provides a minimalistic visualization of the VRP solution, showing the routes and connections between points.

